Using NS-3 : 
    Features : 
        ○ NetAnim
        ○ Visualizer
        ○ WireShark
        ○ TraceMetrics
        ○ FlowMetrics

    Conceptual Abstractions : 
        ○ Node              - A more general term used for host/end-system (Computing devices connected to the network)
                              Node class is used to represent this
                              Think of it as a compputer to which we'll add functionalities like applications, protocol stacks, peripheral cards with their associated drivers etc
       
        ○ Application       - 
        ○ Channel
        ○ Net Device
        ○ Topology Helpers


